\c 113 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 113\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waaqayyo Inni Ol Jedhaan Warra Gad Deebi'an Yaadachuu
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyoon jajadhaa! Isin yaa hojjetoota Waaqayyoo, jajadhaa, maqaa Waaqayyoo jajadhaa.
\m \bd 2\bd* Ammaa jalqabee hamma bara baraatti, maqaan Waaqayyoo eebbifamaa haa ta'u!
\m \bd 3\bd* Ba'a-biiftuutii jalqabee hamma lixa isheetti, maqaan Waaqayyoo jajamaa haa ta'u.
\m \bd 4\bd* Waaqayyo saba lafa irraa hundumaa gararraa dha; ulfinni isaas bantiiwwan waaqaa bira ol in darba!
\m \bd 5\bd* Kan akka Waaqayyo gooftaa keenyaa eenyu? Inni ol gararraa teessoo isaa irra in taa'a.
\m \bd 6\bd* gara bantiiwwan waaqaatti, gara lafaattis gad fageessee in ilaala.
\m \bd 7\bd* Isa gad-deebi'aa awwaara keessaa ol in kaasa, isa dhabaa kosii keessaa ol in fuudha.
\m \bd 8\bd* warra gurguddootaa wajjin, gurguddoota saba isaa wajjinis akka taa'u in godha.
\m \bd 9\bd* Isheen dhabduun haadha ijoollee taatee gammaddee, mana keessa akka jiraattu inni in godha. Waaqayyoon jajadhaa!
\b 
